&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>&lt;a href="https://play.rust-lang.org/?version=stable&amp;amp;mode=debug&amp;amp;edition=2021&amp;amp;gist=7f5ee657d54e102aa7755c32bbdb94c9">playground link&lt;/a>&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>